import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react' const Catalog = () =>{ let [beats, setBeats] = useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ getBeats() },[]) let getBeats = async () =>{ let response = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/beats/') let data = await response.json() console.log(data) setBeats(data) } return ( <>
TITLE
TIME
BPM
TAGS
{beats?.map((beat,index) => (
{beat.title}
2:43
{beat.bpm}
{beat.tags}
))} ) } export default Catalog
